The truth?  Fuck if I know.. outside one simple fact.  Her daughter died because she wasn't around for more than two hours by her own admission.  Two fucking hours.  Did it happen 10 minutes into that 2 hours?  No one knows.. INCLUDING THE FUCKING MOTHER.  She CHOSE to do things other than watch her kid for an inordinate amount of time.<br>
